➜特朗普集会上不戴口罩频繁互动 一把扯下领带扔向观众
http://www.sohu.com/a/424841361_115239	26120
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
